WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.480
The mountains will is clear.

2
00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:04.700
Turn back.

3
00:00:05.860 --> 00:00:11.320
A blast of wind, cold and malicious, strikes like a battering ram.

4
00:00:12.440 --> 00:00:13.760
Kalen is gone.

5
00:00:14.620 --> 00:00:17.940
Her world a dizzying spin toward the abyss.

6
00:00:18.800 --> 00:00:21.820
Then a shadow falls over her.

7
00:00:22.560 --> 00:00:28.680
Viridian, her dying friend, extends a wing not for flight, but for sacrifice.

8
00:00:28.680 --> 00:00:36.860
He becomes her shield, his body screaming in protest as he absorbs the theory meant for them both.

9
00:00:37.380 --> 00:00:38.820
He does not fly.

10
00:00:39.560 --> 00:00:42.520
He endures for her.
